snippet.title: Chhaava | Official Trailer | Vicky K | Rashmika M | Akshaye K | Dinesh Vijan | Laxman U | 14th Feb
snippet.description:
Dinesh Vijan and Maddock Films present the trailer of Hindi Cinema's biggest spectacle ever - #Chhaava

Yeh Sher Shiva ka Chhaava shor nahin karta, seedha shikaar karta hai! 

#ChhaavaTrailer #ChhaavaTrailerOutNow

Releasing in cinemas on 14th February.

Maddock Films presents #Chhaava

snippet.title: Tu Hain Toh Main Hoon | Sky Force | Akshay, Sara, Veer, Tanishk B, Arijit Singh, Afsana Khan, Irshad
snippet.description:
Experience the magic of love with Tu Hai Toh Main Hoon from Sky Force! This soulful melody, sung by Arijit Singh and Afsana Khan, beautifully captures the essence of love and togetherness. Featuring Veer Pahariya and Sara Ali Khan, with lyrics by Irshad Kamil and music by Tanishk Bagchi, this song will surely strike a chord in your heart.

👉 Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Song Credits:
Song name - Tu Hain Toh Main Hoon
Singer - Arijit Singh , Afsana khan
Music - Tanishk Bagchi 
Lyrics - Irshad kamil
Starcast - Veer Pahariya, Sara Ali Khan
Programming - Tanishk Bagchi
Additional Programming- Krishna Kishore
Drums - Stuart Brown ( Scotland ) 
Guitars - Keba Jeremiah 
Nylon Guitars - Ben (Scotland) 
Rhythm - Krishna Kishor 
Woodwinds - Ashish 
Solo Humming - Kamalaja 
Female - Kamalaja, Sri Radha , Fathima 
Dubbing Engineers - Lijesh & Mani Ratnam
Violin Solo-Jeetendra 
Mix and master - Eric Pillai @ Future Sound Of Bombay
Hookline inspired from Mohsen Yeganeh song “Behet Ghol Midam”

Movie Credits:
Produced By: Dinesh Vijan
Produced By: Jyoti Deshpande
Produced By: Amar Kaushik
Producer: Sahil Baber Khan
Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota, Poonam Shivdasani & Komal Kewlani
Written By: Carl Austin (UK), Sandeep Kewlani and Aamil Keeyan Khan
Additional Screenplay & Dialogues By: Niren Bhatt
Director Of Photography: Santhana Krishanan Ravichandran
Director of Choreography- Vijay Ganguly

Lyrics:-

Subhe subhe subhe subhe teri yaadein
Subhe subhe subhe subhe din bana de
Tu meri kheedkiyo pe bikhre din banke
Tu mujhpe dhoop sa hai girta chan chan ke
Chan chan ke

Tu ishq hai toh main baahon mein hoon
Baahon mein hoon toh panaahon mein hoon
Kajal hoon toh main nigahon mein hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Kasme vaade kyun tu hain toh main hoon
Bas main tera hoon tu hain toh main hoon
Seene pe likh loon tu hain toh main hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Antara:
Ek mutthi khwahishon ki tere aage khol ke
Zindagi bhar chup rahoonga baatein dil ki bol ke
Na tere saaye pe bhi aaye koi aanch dua maangoon
Main sadke main tere apni khushi de doonga tol ke

Tu rang mein, teri pehchaan hoon
Pehchaan hoon, main teri jaan hoon
Main koi tera hi armaan hoon
Tu hain toh main hoon

Jhoothe Judaiyan
Jhoothe  bichhode
Yaad kisi ka haath na chhode
Yaad kahe yeh humse aksar
Tu hain toh main hoon

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | PSG 4-2 MAN CITY | Grealish, Haaland Goals | UEFA Champions League
snippet.description:
City will need to beat Club Brugge next week to qualify for the Champions League play-off round after a 4-2 defeat to PSG.
The Blues saw a two -goal lead slip against the impressive French champions who responded with an outstanding fight-back

After a goalless first-half, quickfire second period goals from Jack Grealish and Erling Haaland looked to have set City on the road to a priceless victory.

But two goals in four minutes for PSG wiped out our advantage in the blink of an eye, a third from Joao Neves 12 minutes from time and a Gonçalo Ramos fourth with the last kick of the game gave the Ligue 1 champions a dramatic 4-2 win.

snippet.title: Snow Day Vlog in Tamil | Making a Snow Man | Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this video join me during our recent experience with snow fall. We had never experienced this heavy snow before and we had a great time playing with snow balls and we also built a snowman. Alandra had a great time playing in the snow. We had already protected the cold sensitive plants in the greenhouse and wrapped others. It was a very good experience having snow as a temporary guest and seeing the whole landscape in a bright white color. 

Friends, hope you like today's vlog. See you soon with more interesting vlogs.

snippet.description:
Veera is a unique internet browser that brings you the best and most rewarding browsing experience for the Web3 and the Web2 world all in one fast, smooth, seamless and convenient package for your smartphone. 
With class-leading features like an ad blocker that just can’t be beat, to rewards that make every minute spent on the browser even more gratifying, Veera is re-inventing the way you experience the world wide web.

Download Now- https://xkqzc.app.link/0Zvqf8PwoQb

About the video:

When your bestie becomes the center of attention, things are bound to get complicated! From unexpected glow-ups to hilarious confrontations, this story is packed with comedy, chaos, and emotions. 
And just when you think it’s all over, there’s a zor ka twist at the end that will leave you stunned! 
Don’t miss it, watch till the end!

Sunn Mere Dil Episode 33 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream - Wahaj Ali - Maya Ali - 23rd January 2025 - Har Pal Geo

Sunn Mera Dil Digitally Presented by LUX - Happilac Paints and Ujooba Beauty Cream

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: Chhaava Trailer Review | Vicky Kaushal | Rashmika | Akshay Khanna | RJ Raunak
snippet.description:
#Chhaava #ChhaavaTrailerOutNow #ChhaavaOn14Feb #RJRaunak 

Chhaava, starring Vicky Kaushal, Rashmika Mandanna and Akshaye Khanna, directed by Laxman Utekar dropped its trailer on Wednesday. The trailer of the film presents Vicky as the fearless Maratha warrior, Chhatrapati Sambhaji Maharaj, who took the throne after the death of Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj, the founder of the Maratha empire. The trailer has him waging war against the Mughals, ruled by Aurangzeb, who were trying to take control of the Deccan region after the death of Shivaji. Chhaava means a lion cub.

snippet.title: Mickey 17 | Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
He’s dying to save mankind. #Mickey17 – only in theaters March 7.

From the Academy Award-winning writer/director of “Parasite,” Bong Joon Ho, comes his next groundbreaking cinematic experience, “Mickey 17.” The unlikely hero, Mickey Barnes (Robert Pattinson) has found himself in the extraordinary circumstance of working for an employer who demands the ultimate commitment to the job… to die, for a living.

Written and directed by Bong Joon Ho, “Mickey 17” stars Robert Pattinson (“The Batman,” “Tenet”), Naomi Ackie (“Star Wars: Episode IX – The Rise of Skywalker”), Academy Award nominee Steven Yeun (“Minari,” “Beef”), with Academy Award nominee Toni Collette (“Hereditary”), and Academy Award nominee Mark Ruffalo (“Poor Things”). 

The film is produced by Dede Gardner and Jeremy Kleiner (Oscar winners for “Moonlight” and “12 Years a Slave”), Bong Joon Ho and Dooho Choi (“Okja,” “Snowpiercer”). It is based on the novel Mickey 7 by Edward Ashton. The executive producers are Brad Pitt, Jesse Ehrman, Peter Dodd and Marianne Jenkins. The director of photography is Darius Khondji (Oscar nomination for “Bardo: False Chronicle of a Handful of Truths,” “Okja”). The production designer is Fiona Crombie (Oscar nomination for “The Favourite,” “Cruella”). It is edited by Yang Jinmo (Oscar nomination for “Parasite,” “Okja”). The music is by Jung Jaeil (“Parasite,” “Squid Game”). The visual effects supervisor is Dan Glass (“Fantastic Beasts: The Secrets of Dumbledore,” “Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw”). The costume designer is Catherine George (“Okja,” Snowpiercer”). 

Warner Bros. Pictures presents A Plan B Entertainment Production, An Offscreen Production / A Kate Street Picture Company Production, A Film By Bong Joon Ho: “Mickey 17.” The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, in theaters only nationwide on March 7, 2025, and internationally beginning on 5 March 2025.

snippet.description:

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Anjali wants Taarak to go on a diet and cut down on sweets. She has prepared a salad for him. Jethalal on the other hand, offers lift to Babita who has to attend a function in Bandra. 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 166
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:
#sumanindori #Ashnoorkaur #Zainimam #Sumanindori #serial #devika #Teerath #Suman #anitahassanandanireddy 

Suman Indori: LEAP के बाद नए अंदाज में दिखी सुमन, तीर्थ से बदला लेने के लिए राजनीति में रखा कदम

"Suman Indori" is a heartwarming Indian television serial centered around Suman, a lively and ambitious young woman from Indore. She runs a popular chaat bhandaar, which becomes both her passion and livelihood. The chaat bhandaar reflects her culinary skills and entrepreneurial spirit, attracting customers with its delicious flavors and vibrant atmosphere. The serial beautifully portrays Suman’s journey of managing her business while dealing with the challenges of family expectations, societal norms, and personal aspirations. Her chaat bhandaar not only serves as a backdrop for many emotional and humorous moments but also symbolizes her determination to carve a unique identity. The show weaves themes of family, love, and perseverance, offering a delightful mix of small-town charm and relatable struggles.

snippet.title: Vikrant और Mallika ने बनाया एक Plan! | Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Sneak Peek | Colors TV
snippet.description:
📲 Download JioCinema: https://bit.ly/3Be09Z3

As per Vikrant's plan, Mallika suggests to Aishwarya organising a party to welcome Vikrant's parents. Later, Mallika accompanies Vikrant to Mannat's home to introduce him to her.

Vikrant और Mallika ने बनाया एक Plan! | Mannat Har khushi paane ki | Sneak Peek | Colors TV

-------------------

Abandoned as a newborn by her own heartless mother and raised by her resilient maasi, Shruti, Mannat grows up to be a passionate and ambitious chef, unaware of her mysterious origins. Her journey intertwines with that of Vikrant, a successful buisnessman (restaurateur), as they bond over their love for cooking amidst the vibrant backdrop of Mumbai's chawls and elite culinary spaces. Mannat’s biological mother is none other than Aishwarya, a wealthy and manipulative woman determined to keep her secrets buried who is also Mannat's boss at Mezbaani where she works as a junior chef. Life takes a dramatic turn when Mannat discovers Shruti is not her biological mother, propelling her on a desperate quest to save Shruti’s life by finding her real mother for a liver transplant. Amidst these revelations, Mannat finds her strongest support in Vikrant, the prince charming of her life, who stands by her side, offering unwavering encouragement as she navigates the challenges life throws her way. As Mannat’s rising career, Shruti’s failing health, and the revelations of a hidden past collide, Mannat faces a whirlwind of love, betrayal, and self-discovery. Will her dreams and resilience help her overcome the storm, or will the weight of her past keep her from achieving her destiny?


Main Cast and Their Characters:
Ayesha Singh as Mannat
Adnan Khan(Vikrant
Mona Vasu as Aishwarya
Sharain Khanduja as Mallika
Mamta Verma as Shruti
Delnaaz Irani as Harneet
Hasan Zaidi as Gagan
Karan Godhwami as Puneet
Swati Anand as Neetu
Rushad Rana as Rony
